SQL_STMT_U.val: select AMOUNT_PRESOLD, AMOUNT_NOTSOLD, AMOUNT_FINANCED from (select cast(sum(A.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) as AMOUNT_PRESOLD from :1/CLSD A where A.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and A.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'Y') as PRESOLD, (select cast(sum(B.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) as AMOUNT_NOTSOLD from :1/CLSD B where B.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and B.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'N') as NOTSOLD, (select cast(sum(C.CLSD_FINANCEAMOUNT) as decimal (17,2)) as AMOUNT_FINANCED from :1/CLSD C where C.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2) as FINANCED for fetch only

select A.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE as ARTICLE_TYPE, (select cast(sum(B.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) from :1/CLSD B where B.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and B.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'Y' and B.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE = A.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE) as AMOUNT_PRESOLD, (select cast(sum(C.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) from :1/CLSD C where C.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and C.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'N' and C.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE = A.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE) as AMOUNT_NOTSOLD, cast(sum(A.CLSD_FINANCEAMOUNT) as decimal (17,2)) AMOUNT_FINANCED from :1/CLSD A where A.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 group by A.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE order by A.CLSD_ARTICLETYPE for fetch only

select A.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE as ARTICLE_GROUPCODE, (select cast(sum(B.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) from :1/CLSD B where B.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and B.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'Y' and B.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE = A.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE) as AMOUNT_PRESOLD, (select cast(sum(C.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) from :1/CLSD C where C.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and C.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'N' and C.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE = A.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE) as AMOUNT_NOTSOLD, cast(sum(A.CLSD_FINANCEAMOUNT) as decimal (17,2)) AMOUNT_FINANCED from :1/CLSD A where A.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 group by A.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE order by A.CLSD_ARTICLEGROUPCODE for fetch only

select A.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY as ARTICLE_LOCATION_COUNTRY, (select cast(sum(B.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) from :1/CLSD B where B.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and B.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'Y' and B.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY = A.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY) as AMOUNT_PRESOLD, (select cast(sum(C.CLSD_LCMTOTALVALUEBC) as decimal (17,2)) from :1/CLSD C where C.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 and C.CLSD_PRESOLD = 'N' and C.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY = A.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY) as AMOUNT_NOTSOLD, cast(sum(A.CLSD_FINANCEAMOUNT) as decimal (17,2)) AMOUNT_FINANCED from :1/CLSD A where A.CLSD_NFIR_NO = :2 group by A.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY order by A.CLSD_ARTICLELOCATIONCOUNTRY for fetch only
